						<div class="postbody">The stack overflow display is a neat idea. I have one byte at $01BF that I check once a frame for a stack overflow (Stack shouldn't go deeper than $01C0), but I hadn't thought of displaying the stack on error. You could expand this, I assume, for a debug view - the ability to display any page of memory at any time.<br /><br />I can see a line and can make it scroll to the right. Should anything else be happening?</div>

