			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I considered bitwise majority of previous, new read #1, and new read #2, but that can cause spurious Up+Down presses.<br /><br />Hold Up + Left, then within a frame move to Down + Left.<br /><br />Previous: Up + Left<br />Read #1: Down + Left<br />Read #2: Bit deletion prior to Up makes it appear as Up + Down<br />Result: Majority for Up, majority for Down, majority for Left<br /><br />So instead, I just go with new read #1 if new read #1 == new read #2 else previous.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
